        {
            "title": "聯合利華將凍結全球招聘 伊朗戰爭推高運輸成本",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於伊朗戰爭導致成本上升，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯合利華\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯合利華;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯合利華\">聯合利華</a>將在全球凍結招聘三個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項舉措是這家多芬(Dove)肥皂製造商更廣泛縮減開支計畫的一部分，其中還包括裁員和調整獎金結構。與此同時，聯合利華正與美國調味料製造商McCormick &amp; Co.就出售其大部分食品業務深入談判。路透周一晚些時候率先報導了招聘凍結的消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發言人在聲明中表示，鑑於外部環境充滿不確定性，聯合利華決定暫時停止招聘，並補充指出，聯合利華依然是一家靈活的企業，並將隨時根據需要調整計畫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c0fb8f90-166f-3caa-975b-c3ba8e6eac7a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於中東衝突，消費品公司正面臨飆升的成本，貨運和遠洋輪船因能源價格大漲而加收附加費。此外，塑膠包裝以及用於清潔劑和洗髮精等產品的原料，生產成本也變得更加昂貴。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利分析師Sarah Simon上周在一份報告中指出，聯合利華可能特別容易受到伊朗戰爭的影響，其雄心勃勃的銷售量成長目標依賴印度等國家——但印度極易受到液化天然氣成本上升和供應減少的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Unilever to Freeze Hiring as Iran War Drives Up Shipping Costs</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E8%8F%AF%E5%B0%87%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E6%8E%A8%E9%AB%98%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC-080202773.html",
